{"tid":1534533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復香港」→「香港獨立」","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:22:15.000Z","uid":308233,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d5bd2ebeb579493375e93659e0fb12c32e1faf","tid":1534533,"uid":308233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n呢句係梁天琦嘅競選口號<br />\n諗出嚟嘅原因係因為要參選<br />\n所以要避嫌，驚比人DQ<br />\n而唔講「香港獨立」<br />\n去到今時今日，仲有人相信一國兩制<br />\n簡直係天大嘅笑話<br />\n仲有人驚所謂嘅「激嬲共產黨」<br />\n會唔會太可笑？<br />\n口口聲聲話Hong Kong is not China<br />\n但唔敢講「香港獨立」？<br />\n其實唯一出路，只有獨立<br />\n一日比共產黨統治<br />\n一日比一日危險<br />\n我相信天琦都想我地講「香港獨立」<br />\n而唔係「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n我地而家有得講唔講<br />\n而自己滅自己聲<br />\n<br />\n希望下次遊行可以有人同我一齊嗌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立！</span></span><br />\n展示比國際睇我地嘅決心<br />\n其實Trump清朝債劵果招<br />\n已經暗示我地可以獨立<br />\n自己都唔出聲<br />\n叫人地點幫你<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n如果呢四個字都唔敢嗌<br />\n我都無咩好講<br />\n只可以話抵輸<br />\n香港人只配做共產黨嘅奴隸"},{"pid":"708366d322ec0a8e5941c4b661b8afd385766c2e","tid":1534533,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c916a505ff31533202721aec7b3dd15584b82f1","tid":1534533,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:40.000Z","msg":"[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有冇人識831太子車廂嘅人 佢哋出嚟先可以拎CCTV 睇下有冇人死</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個撚個話關心義士 去太子送花<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFOWARD去各大tg group/tg channel問下有冇人識當日太子站手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋遲一秒佢哋就del多秒"},{"pid":"df2f1d833e10c360a546e680b0a738153d1265cb","tid":1534533,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:40:00.000Z","msg":"獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1b6e4088a3aa3bf3bf16e69a6544e86000b996","tid":1534533,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"［現在公開可能な情報］9月到底抱咩心態去做人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534243</a><br />\n跪求一閱"},{"pid":"61e2bec2d32bad9da722e99146c5080783771b61","tid":1534533,"uid":93060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"回歸中華民國"},{"pid":"11036dcfe0939a283864e6a1d44aa7c222960331","tid":1534533,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"2131153a3c04b3ab8b0bf75bba6d517ab8821280","tid":1534533,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"1adab26f1df7227d7db4b18777aa54276a9f3030","tid":1534533,"uid":266874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"8fda0742582ea5b0a927d4bef51013f1241a9ef8","tid":1534533,"uid":308233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"估唔居然有咁多人負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}